{"tid":449694,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)鬼船 死神凶盒 恐怖遊輪 忌日快樂","createTime":"2017-10-27T11:50:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-27T17:33:59.000Z","uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a28c28b6504b65bc21551b20ce4cb1d8619ae7f7","tid":449694,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T11:50:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=ueduJ9UI%2FfU5gbN3igvYfsn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=07454fcf\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> V台入佢主頁睇先比較順<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=ueduJ9UI%2FfU5gbN3igvYfsn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=917a0256\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/5/55/Ghost_Ship_poster.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fen%2F5%2F55%2FGhost_Ship_poster.JPG&h=f86217e6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://assets.wmoov.com/movie/photo/201708/p2460025207_1504187002.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fassets.wmoov.com%2Fmovie%2Fphoto%2F201708%2Fp2460025207_1504187002.jpg&h=2037d045&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/b/b4/Triangle_(Christopher_Smith).jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fb%2Fb4%2FTriangle_%28Christopher_Smith%29.jpg&h=87a097be&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/f/f8/Happy_Death_Day_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Ff%2Ff8%2FHappy_Death_Day_Poster.jpg&h=57840a0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.安東妮雅葛莎號，是1954年在熱拿亞船塢建造的巨型遊輪，裝潢設備卻極盡奢華，被喻為人類史上第一座海上皇宮。這艘海上宮殿的保險由倫敦的羅氏保險公司所承保，並於1962年5月21日在拉布拉多半島海岸外失蹤。 非常奇怪的是，它並沒有發出求救信號或跟任何船隻通話，它就這樣憑空消失得無影無蹤。從那一天起，世上每一名打撈船長以及每一位乘客的親人都在尋找它，希望『安東妮雅葛莎號』並沒有沉船。 四十年的時間很快過去，『安東妮雅葛莎號』失蹤疑雲也在人們的記憶中漸漸變得模糊...<br />\n<br />\n2.高中生嘉兒（祖兒京治 飾）一直活喺媽媽自殺嘅陰影之下，喺學校又遭受欺凌，生活十分不順。有日佢偶爾發現，爸爸（賴恩菲臘 飾）從垃圾堆中執返嚟嘅音樂盒可以幫佢實現7個願望，於是半信半疑嘅佢對住盒子許願。點知願望竟然一一成真，金錢、人緣、愛情&hellip;&hellip;要乜有乜<br />\n<br />\n3.潔西（梅麗莎&middot;喬治飾）是一個單身母親，有一個患有自閉症的兒子湯米。她的朋友格雷格（麥可&middot;多爾曼飾）邀請她周末一起乘「三角洲號」遊艇出海遊玩，同行的還有海瑟（艾瑪&middot;朗飾）、薩莉（雷切爾&middot;卡爾帕尼飾）、唐尼（亨利&middot;尼克森飾）、維克多（利亞姆&middot;海莫斯沃斯飾）。出海不久，潔西內心始終籠罩著一股不祥預感，正當大夥沉浸在歡樂的派對氣氛時，埋伏潔西腦海的擔憂竟然成真&hellip;原本萬里無雲的好天氣驟轉成狂風暴雨，遊艇也在驚滔駭浪的摧殘下翻覆。遇難的眾人只好登上一艘航行經過的郵輪尋求協助。但是，登船後，潔西卻對郵輪上的一切感到似曾相識，一行人也開始接二連三地目睹地獄般的殘虐景象，甚至遭遇蒙面殺人狂的追殺，一連串超乎常理的神祕事件，逐步將眾人推往萬劫不復的恐怖輪迴中&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n4.故事描述女大生崔莉&middot;吉曼在過生日的當天遭人謀殺，且也因此陷入時間循環而不斷地重新回到那令人恐懼的一天，這使崔莉決定利用這現象來找出殺死自己的兇手<br />\n<br />\n8 15PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=ueduJ9UI%2FfU5gbN3igvYfsn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=e29402c3\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=ueduJ9UI%2FfU5gbN3igvYfsn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=54ad787e\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4e6df1826f5d5b87fdcae5abec52f0fb457007b","tid":449694,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T11:54:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d49ab1bfb16ff808d6adab200417392226bcffd5","tid":449694,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T12:19:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bc0ebff5f5f71038503aa71685dd210f460d72e","tid":449694,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T12:33:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f724c10601fcc4eee0a4dd733da20e6e2e6f553","tid":449694,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T13:10:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57cbc6f3eef51f1b04070796a84262dc984ecec2","tid":449694,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T14:34:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a93d2a199eba486a5514f50a03858cf47702eaed","tid":449694,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T15:41:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cde9e1fd7f009564054f1146a5accf1c3a3de537","tid":449694,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T15:59:09.000Z","msg":"<i